descriptionHtml:
So heres just some werewolf mods to make em look a bit more like cats..i should probably do a tiger one but im too tired, anyway they have cat ears now and untill the creation kit comes out youll have to stick with the wolf tails

The skyrim game doesnt originally have a cheetah snow leopard or a panther , its just the name of the folder to distinguish which textures are which, just open the folder and carry the werewolf folder to the path steam/steamapps/common/skyrim/data/textures/actors/character
Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data\\textures\\actors\\character
author: DigitalLion
